Whether there was a change of employment;
Whether the change of employment was voluntary;
When and why the employment with the original employer ended; and
What steps you and your new employer took after the change of employment to file an adjustment of status application or apply for an immigrant visa. We may excuse a failure to timely file in cases of both voluntary and involuntary change of employment when considering the totality of the circumstances.

